rm -rf XP-BLUP &&
git clone https://github.com/tanglab/XP-BLUP.git &&
cd XP-BLUP &&
chmod +x *.sh &&
wget -qO- https://s3.amazonaws.com/plink1-assets/plink_linux_x86_64_20241013.zip > plink.zip &&
unzip -o plink.zip &&
mkdir -p bin &&
mv plink bin/ &&
rm plink.zip &&

mv gcta-1.94.4-linux-kernel-3-x86_64/gcta64 bin/ &&
rm -rf gcta64.zip gcta-1.94.4-linux-kernel-3-x86_64 &&
export PATH=$PATH:$PWD/bin
